1. Download Python
2. Selenium
   ~ pip install selenium
3. WebDrivers
   ~ Chrome Driver
   ~ Firefox Driver (GeckoDriver)
4. Pycharm studio download
5. pytest framework
   ~ pip install pytest
   ~ pip install --upgrade pytest
6. Fixture & Conftest.py
   ~ Conftest.py to store the fixture & html report modifications & Browsers initialization
7. Pytest Html Report
   ~ pip install pytest-html (to download the package) , â€“html=report.html (to download the report)
   ~ pytest .\src\PageObjectModel\Tests\LoginPage_test.py -v --html=./gmail.html - To run you test cases with HTML report
8. To parallel testing
   ~ pip install pytest-xdist
9. To install web driver manager
   ~ pip install webdriver_manager
10. To upgrade PIP
   ~ python.exe -m pip install --upgrade pip
11. To install allure report
   ~ pip install allure-pytest
12. To uninstall allure report
   ~ pip uninstall allure-pytest
13. To upgrade allure report
   ~ pip install --upgrade allure-pytest
14. To generate allure report with your test case - Parallel execution
   ~ pytest -n auto --alluredir=allure-results\
15. To check the allure report
   ~ allure serve allure-results
